\id GEN
\imt1 INTRODUCCIÓN
\is1 Importancia del evangelio de Marcos
\ip \bk The Acts of the Apostles\bk* is a continuation of \bk The Gospel according to Luke\bk*
\c 1
\cl Psalm One
\cp A
\v 1 You are to engrave on it as on a seal: 
\b
\pc HOLY TO THE LORD.\f + \fr 28:36 \fl OR \ft That is, the LORD but some mss do not have \fq the Son of God. \fqa Whoever\f* 
\v 2 ‘Cursed is the man who makes a carved idol or molten image—an abomination to the LORD, the work of the hands of a craftsman—and sets it up in secret.’ 
\qr And let all the \bd people\bd* say, ‘Amen!’

